videos.description: Grayson Allen makes a quick long 3-pointer to extend Duke's lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Allen sinks long 3-pointer early

videos.description: Grayson Allen goes to intercept a pass and then chases down the ball along with Justin Robinson.
videos.headline: Allen involved in small scuffle

videos.description: Grayson Allen turns the ball over and Nickeil Alexander-Walker lays it up on the other end for Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Hokies' steal-and-score adds to first half run

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. grabs an offensive board and slams it down for Duke.
videos.headline: Carter throws down putback slam

videos.description: Justin Robinson outhustles the defense and draws contact on the layup for the Hokies.
videos.headline: Robinson blows by defense on layup

videos.description: Chris Clarke forces a turnover and lays it up on the other end to make it a one-point game with less than a minute to go.
videos.headline: Clarke's steal-and-score draws VT close to Duke

videos.description: Chris Clarke breaks down how the Hokies were able to score with just seconds remaining to take down the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Clarke breaks down final possession to upset No. 5 Duke

videos.description: Virginia Tech fans rain jeers down at the refs after a foul is called on the Hokies. Head coach Buzz Williams goes to center court and tells the students to stop cursing and stop throwing things on the court.
videos.headline: Williams implores Virginia Tech students to 'quit cussing'

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams implores Virginia Tech students to 'quit cussing') 2018/02/26 ESHEET

videos.description: Chris Clarke scores with under 10 seconds remaining to give the Hokies the lead. On the other end, Grayson Allen's 3-point heave is no good, as the No. 5 Blue Devils fall 64-63.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech takes down Duke
